{"tid":1644350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各位手足，同自己許下一個承諾 今生今世都唔會原諒呢班差佬","createTime":"2019-10-10T13:54:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T14:55:39.000Z","uid":41601,"like":35,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"65f6cf944f25caaf57e4a55eadcfea2211502e11","tid":1644350,"uid":41601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:54:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">段崇智</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我諗正常男人聽到啲風化案既女事主經過都會嬲到仆街<br />\n<br />\n我<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母呀</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n聽撚完仲話我之後再同你傾傾？<br />\n係咪要知晒啲細節呀？ 根本就再對受害人造成二次傷害<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我真係未撚見過啲咁仆街既校長<br />\n我都慶幸我無揀入中大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲們<br />\n今生今世就算因爲仇恨憎恨而要落地獄<br />\n都要每日同自己講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我今生今世都唔會原諒所有Popo</span></span>"},{"pid":"5d4071d75a1092fbb5ba16c6d85cc47b9469bbc0","tid":1644350,"uid":41601,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:56:49.000Z","msg":"仲有呀 江狗唔好唔記得自己講過咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2019年8月30日：警方今天的每日例行記者會，有記者問到有人指控在被捕後遭警方性侵。江永祥回應指，匿名指控如此嚴重，如果接納，會世界大亂。並回應說，近期社會湧現很多不願意挺身而出、匿名的針對警方的投訴，而有關指控完全沒有理據支持，警方是理所當然否定"},{"pid":"b8625ef6279bdfb670e5314ce8c82f909a960568","tid":1644350,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T14:00:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce80f0d08b6438d445539a98f7e1edd7ccac5531","tid":1644350,"uid":41601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T14:02:28.000Z","msg":"你收嗲啦 三毛<br />\n同謝蛇一齊共享大灣區福利未呀"},{"pid":"56d0c7df657c98d480b8f28a6b1d4e62d0068155","tid":1644350,"uid":322796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T14:03:40.000Z","msg":"今生今世 deal<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=